				p.col-md-8.lead.text-center The future holds better returns, and the key to the future lies in a better understanding of the past. 
			.row#team
				h1.text-center Our Team 
				p.col-md-8.lead.text-center Mexico, Italy, East Coast and West Coast: our team brings together a unique blend of culture and experience that propels our mission forward! Algorithms, securities, programming and finance barely scrape the surface of the nuanced and fascinating challenges our team tackles with hard work and creativity. 
				.contact-holder
