				.contact-holder
					contact-image-holder
						img(src="assets/ryan.png" alt="Ryan's pic").img-circle.img-responsive
					h3.text-center VP of Business Development
					hr 
					.content
						b Ryan
						|  is a LA native who brings his West Coast charm to the team. After graduating from CSU and UCLA, he forged his own path as investment research professional, acquiring critical experience from all levels of the financial industry along the way. After moving to Palo Alto and meeting Lorenzo, he joined Alpha-Sci in order to expose his extensive network to alpha-sci's revolutionary technology. When he is not making new friends and keeping in touch with his old ones, he nerds out with Lorenzo by talking about derivatives, prominent players in finance, and most importantly: Bitcoin.  
